annexed by indonesia in 1976 
the pope arrived after a weekend visit to seoul south korea 
the pontiff knelt and kissed the tarmac wet from a tropical 
rainstorm in the sticky 90 degree heat 
soldiers lined the 10mile motorcade route from the military 
airport to the palm treeringed presidential palace where 
